These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, banana
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the person eating banana##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | banana   | cabbage  |
| Sport   | handball | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, raspberry
2 different pets are kept: fish, rat
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the fish is not the person eating raspberry##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | cabbage | raspberry      |
| Pet    | fish  | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
