.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, crime
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, badminton
1. the person watching crime movies is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
2. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | crime |
| Sport         | badminton | rugby      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
