There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, thai
1. the fan reggae is on the far right##1
2. the fan disco is not the spanish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | reggae      |
| Nationality   | thai | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, teacher
2 different pets are kept: snake, ferret
1. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
2. the security-guard is not the owner of the ferret##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | security-guard | teacher |
| Pet   | snake       | ferret       |

 #################################

 
